Repository for bash repo.

File Extension
==============
EXT=${1##*.}

Where $1 is filename to get extension from.

Basename
========
ls | sed 's/\(.*\)\..*/\1/'

  or

BASENAME=${1%\.*}

Where $1 is the filename to get basename from.


Filelist
========
loop-over-files.txt
  Loop over files using find


